    'Offshore waters of the subtropical zone of the Atlantic, bordering the Canary Islands, Madeira, the Azores, the Mediterraneo-Atlantic coasts of Iberia, the Mediterraneo-Atlantic and Saharo-Atlantic coasts of Africa, south to Cap Blanc. ', '(Nelson, 1980: 25-28; Lofgren, 1984: 22-23).');
    'Offshore waters of the Mediterranean Sea.', '(Nelson, 1980: 25-28; Miller, 1983; Ben-Tuvia, 1983; Lofgren, 1984: 22-23; Draganovic, 1996; Schembri, 1999a).');
