    'Communities of [Limonium gmelinii] and [Artemisia santonicum] with [Aster tripolium], [Spergularia media], [Hordeum hystrix], [Gypsophila muralis] var. [stepposa], of the lower Danube basin and of northern Thrace.
', '(Sanda y al., 1980; So¢, 1980; Sanda and Popescu, 1990a).');
    'Salt-meadow communities of medium tall often tussock-forming grasses, sedges or rushes of the western Black Sea and lower Danube plains, with local representatives in the northern Thracian middle Maritsa and Tundzha basins. ', '(Ganchev y al., 1971; Sanda y al., 1980).');
