    'Formations of western Black Sea saltmarshes dominated by [Juncus maritimus], [Juncus acutus] or [Juncus littoralis], with [Limonium latifolium], [Puccinellia distans], [Plantago maritima], [Juncus gerardi], [Aster tripolium].', '(Krausch, 1965; Ganchev y al., 1971; Sanda y al., 1980; Popescu y al. 1992).');
