    'Formations of eastern Andalusia (Armeria, Granada) dominated by, or rich in, [Centaurea hyssopifolia], [Jurinea pinnata] or [Gypsophila struthium]. ', '(Rivas Goday, 1955; Rivas Goday and Rivas-Martinez, 1968; Rivas-Martinez and Costa, 1970; Bellot Rodriquez, 1979; Peinado Lorca and Rivas-Martinez, 1987).');
    'Formations of the central Duero with [Linum suffruticosum] and [Lepidium subulatum].  ', '(Rivas Goday, 1955; Rivas Goday and Rivas-Martinez, 1968; Rivas-Martinez and Costa, 1970; Bellot Rodriquez, 1979; Peinado Lorca and Rivas-Martinez, 1987).');
    'Open low garrigues of eroded gypsiferous hills of the Ebro basin and of the upper Turia region, with [Gypsophila hispanica].  ', '(Rivas Goday, 1955; Delvosalle and Duvigneaud, 1962; Rivas Goday and Rivas-Martinez, 1968; Bolos, 1973; Bellot Rodriquez, 1979; Géhu, 1984a; Peinado Lorca and Rivas-Martinez, 1987).');
    'Open formations of gypsiferous hills of the Ebro basin and of the upper Turia region dominated by, or very rich in, [Gypsophila hispanica], the most widespread northeastern gypsum scrub component.  ', '(Rivas Goday, 1955; Delvosalle and Duvigneaud, 1962; Rivas Goday and Rivas-Martinez, 1968; Bolos, 1973; Bellot Rodriquez, 1979; Peinado Lorca and Rivas-Martinez, 1987).');
    'Formations of [Helianthemum squamatum] of gypsiferous hills of the Ebro basin and of the upper Turia region, often very homogeneous.  ', '(Rivas Goday, 1955; Delvosalle and Duvigneaud, 1962; Rivas Goday and Rivas-Martinez, 1968; Bolos, 1973; Bellot Rodriquez, 1979; Peinado Lorca and Rivas-Martinez, 1987).');
    'Formations of somewhat deeper calcaro-gypsiferous soils of hills of the Ebro basin and of the upper Turia region, rich in [Ononis tridentata].  ', '(Rivas Goday, 1955; Delvosalle and Duvigneaud, 1962; Rivas Goday and Rivas-Martinez, 1968; Bolos, 1973; Bellot Rodriquez, 1979; Peinado Lorca and Rivas-Martinez, 1987).');
