    'Formations of the Sierras de Cazorla, Segura, Alcaraz, Taibilla of the high Guadalquivir basin, with [Erodium cazorlanum], [Scorzonera albicans].  ', '(Rivas Goday and Rivas-Martinez, 1968; Izco, 1979; Peinado Lorca and Rivas-Martinez, 1987).');
    'Formations of the sierras Tejeda, Almijara, la Torrecilla, Harana, Baza, la Sagra, Cazulas, Lapeza and of the Serrania de Ronda with [Anthyllis vulneraria] ssp. [argyrophylla], [Anthyllis tejedensis], [Helianthemum viscidulum].  ', '(Rivas Goday and Rivas-Martinez, 1968; Izco, 1979; Peinado Lorca and Rivas-Martinez, 1987).');
    'Formations of the Sierra de Magina with [Helianthemum pannosum] ssp. [frigidulum], [Lithodora nitida] and [Viola cazorlensis].  ', '(Rivas Goday and Rivas-Martinez, 1968; Izco, 1979; Peinado Lorca and Rivas-Martinez, 1987).');
