    'Isolated, endemic-rich, mostly summital hedgehog-heaths of calcareous mountains of Aegean islands and Mount Athos. ', '(Rechinger, 1943, 1951; Polunin, 1980; Reisigl y al., 1980; Polunin and Walters, 1985; Noirfalise, 1987).');
