    'Mesophile, flower-rich [Carex sempervirens] and [Festuca calva] grasslands of the subalpine and lower alpine levels of the Dolomites, the Venetian and Carnic Alps, the Karawanken, the Julian and Steiner Alps.', '(Grabherr y al., 1993: 421-423; Seliskar, 1998: 16).');
