    'Steppes of Transbaikalia, Outer Mongolia, Inner Mongolia, the Songnen Plain of Northeast China, the western Loess Plateau of North China, mountain steppes of the Tien Shan, from the rim of the Naryn and Isyk-K¿l basins eastwards, of the Sayan and Tannu mountains.', '(Saphronova, 1964b: units 63-71; Saphronova, 1964c: units 84-89; Walter, 1974: 165, units 6-9; Kovar and Volkova, 1981: 125-132; Ehrenreich y al., 1982: 45-46; Mei''e y al., 1985: 152-153; Walter and Breckle, 1986: 184-189, 232; Knapp and Sancir, 1986).');
