    'Steppes of the Anatolian Plateau, of Transcaucasia, of the eastern cis-Caucasian hills of Daghestan and the Terek basin, of the Iranian Plateau, the Kopet Dagh, the Pamir-Alai, the extreme western Tien-Shan, around the rim of the Ferghana basin and along the spur of the Karatau, and of northern Mesopotamia.', '(Saphronova, 1964a: unit 52; Saphronova, 1964b: units 51, 53, 54, 55, 57; Saphronova, 1964c: 73, 74, 75, 76; Zohary, 1973; Walter, 1974: 256-283, 369, unit IV; Walter and Breckle, 1986, 1991c; Korotkov y al., 1991).');
