    'Neutrophile [Fagus sylvatica-Abies alba] forests of the montane zone of the western Carpathians, with [Cardamine glandulosa] ([Dentaria glandulosa]), [Cardamine bulbifera] ([Dentaria bulbifera]), [Galium odoratum], [Salvia glutinosa], [Symphytum cordatum], [Symphytum tuberosum], [Euphorbia amigdales], [Glechoma hirsuta]. ', '(Moravec y al., 1982: 6; Somsak, 1983; Matuszkiewicz, 1984; Moravec, 1998a: 125-128, unit 19).');
