    'Screens or veils of perennial tall herbs, small bushes and lianas lining lowland watercourses, and sometimes other water bodies, often with many ruderal and exogenous plants.  ', '(Soo, 1961, 1980; Ellenberg, 1963; Duvigneaud, 1967; Guinochet and Vilmorin, 1973; Géhu and Géhu, 1976; Sanda y al., 1980: 104; Moravec y al., 1983: 93-94; Matuszkiewicz, 1984: 70; Géhu, 1984a; Drachenfels y al., 1984; Ellenberg, 1988: 305-307; Oberdorfer, 1990; Korotkov y al., 1991: 145-146; Seliskar, 1998: 12).');
