    'Tall herb-dominated communities of Scandinavian mountains dominated by [Cicerbita alpina], [Geranium sylvaticum], [Cirsium helenioides] with [Aconitum septentrionale], [Angelica archangelica], [Ranunculus platanifolia], [Saussurea alpina], [Rumex acetosa], [Trollius europaeus], [Anthoxanthum odoratum], [Calamagrostis purpurea], [Deschampsia cespitosa], [Poa alpina], [Equisetum arvense], [Equisetum pratense], [Athyrium filix-femina], [Matteuccia struthiopteris], [Rubus saxatilis], [Salix spp.]; they colonize slopes and steep hillsides at subalpine and lower alpine levels.', '(Nordiska ministerradet, 1984: unit 1.3.6.1; Påhlsson, 1994: unit 1.2.6.1).');
