    'Lowland and montane mesophile pastures and hay meadows of the boreal, nemoral, warm-temperate humid, Irano-Turanian and mediterranean zones. ', '(Soo, 1961, 1980; Ellenberg, 1963, 1988; Horvat y al., 1974; Westhoff and den Held, 1975; Walter and Breckle, 1986, 1991c; Peinado Lorca and Rivas-Martinez, 1987; Korotkov y al., 1991; Oberdorfer, 1993b; Ellmauer and Mucina, 1993).');
    'Regularly grazed mesophile pastures of Europe, fertilized and on well-drained soils, with [Lolium perenne], [Cynosurus cristatus], [Poa spp.], [Festuca spp.], [Trifolium repens], [Leontodon autumnalis], [Bellis perennis], [Ranunculus repens], [Ranunculus acris], [Cardamine pratensis]; they are most characteristic of the Euro-Siberian zone, but extend to Atlantic Iberia and the Cordillera Central, the Apennines and the supra-Mediterranean zone of the Balkan peninsula and Greece.', '(Zeidler, 1954; Ellenberg, 1963, 1988; Ahtarov, 1964a; Guinochet and Vilmorin, 1973; Horvat y al., 1974; Westhoff and den Held, 1975; Bournérias, 1979, 1984; Soo, 1980; Noirfalise y al., 1980, 1985; Fuller, 1982; Moravec y al., 1983; Matuszkiewicz, 1984; Rivas-Martinez y al., 1984b; Rivas-Martinez y al., 1987; Loidi Arregui, 1987; Oberdorfer, 1990; Korotkov y al., 1991; Rodwell, 1992: units MG5, MG6; Meshinev y al., 1993: 131; Seliskar, 1998: 17).');
    'Continuous pastureland of Euro-Siberian Europe, Atlantic Iberia and the Cordillera Central, the Apennines and the supra-Mediterranean zone of the Balkan peninsula and Greece, unrelieved by networks of ditches. ', '(Zeidler, 1954; Ellenberg, 1963, 1988; Ahtarov, 1964a; Guinochet and Vilmorin, 1973; Horvat y al., 1974; Westhoff and den Held, 1975; Bournérias, 1979, 1984; Soo, 1980; Noirfalise y al., 1980, 1985; Fuller, 1982; Moravec y al., 1983; Matuszkiewicz, 1984; Rivas-Martinez y al., 1984b; Rivas-Martinez y al., 1987; Loidi Arregui, 1987; Oberdorfer, 1990; Korotkov y al., 1991; Rodwell, 1992: units MG5, MG6; Meshinev y al., 1993: 131).');
    'Relatively species-poor grasslands of Euro-Siberian Western and Central Europe, Atlantic Iberia and the Cordillera Central, the Apennines and the supra-Mediterranean zone of the Balkan peninsula and Greece dominated by [Lolium perenne], often with [Cynosurus cristatus].  ', '(Lebrun y al., 1949: unit 132; Zeidler, 1954; Ellenberg, 1963, 1988; Ahtarov, 1964a; Thill, 1964: 49; Guinochet and Vilmorin, 1973; Horvat y al., 1974: 270, 398-400, 489; Matuszkiewicz and Matuszkiewicz, 1975: 106; Westhoff and den Held, 1975; Bournérias, 1979, 1984; Soo, 1980; Noirfalise y al., 1980, 1985; Fuller, 1982; Moravec y al., 1983; Matuszkiewicz, 1984; Rivas-Martinez y al., 1984b; Rivas-Martinez y al., 1987; Loidi Arregui, 1987; Delescaille, 1987: 76; Oberdorfer, 1990; Rodwell, 1992: unit MG6; Meshinev y al., 1993: 131; Seliskar, 1998: 17; Hoda y al., 1998: 10).');
    'More species-rich grasslands of the British Isles dominated by [Cynosurus cristatus] and with many flowering herbs, notably [Centaurea nigra].  ', '(Fuller, 1982; Rodwell, 1992: unit MG5).');
    'Pastures mostly of uplands of Western Europe, Central Europe and Eastern Europe, less treated, rougher and more species-rich than those of unit 38.111, often with the cespitose [Festuca nigrescens] and a significant representation of nitrofuge species. ', '(Lebrun y al., 1949: unit 135; Zeidler, 1954; Ellenberg, 1963, 1988; Ahtarov, 1964a; Guinochet and Vilmorin, 1973; Horvat y al., 1974; Westhoff and den Held, 1975; Bournérias, 1979, 1984; Soo, 1980; De Sloover y al., 1980: 46-48; Noirfalise y al., 1980, 1985; Moravec y al., 1983; Matuszkiewicz, 1984; Rivas-Martinez y al., 1984b; Rivas-Martinez y al., 1987; Loidi Arregui, 1987; Oberdorfer, 1990; Korotkov y al., 1991: 163; Meshinev y al., 1993: 131; Seliskar, 1998: 17).');
