    '[Juniperus excelsa]-dominated forest formations, accompanied by Mediterranean brush, maquis or garrigues in the undergrowth, forming locally bin Meso-Mediterranean enclaves of the Pontic Ranges as well as in Aegean and East-Mediterranean southern Anatolia.', '(Noirfalise, 1987: units M8a, M10). ');
