    'Formations of the upper montane and supra-Mediterranean levels of Iberia dominated by the endemic [Betula celtiberica]. ', '(Diaz Gonzalez and Fernandez Prieto, 1987; Navarro Andres and Valle Gutierrez, 1987; Izco, 1987; Rivas-Martinez y al., 1987).');
