    'Plantations of [Abies nordmanniana] in the Caucasus, of [Abies bornmuelleriana], [Abies equi-trojani] or [Abies nordmanniana] in the Pontic system, of [Abies cilicica] in the Taurus system.', '(Davis, 1965; Zohary, 1973; Walter, 1974; Rushforth, 1987).');
