    'Calcareous cliff and rock communities of the mountains and uplands of the boreal and arctic zones of the central Palaearctic domaine. Included are the communities of the Chibiny range, of the Urals, of the chains of northern central Siberia, from the Putorany to the Tscherski range and of the mountains of southern Siberia, from the Altai to the Stanowoi range.', '(Birot, 1970; Walter, 1974).');
