    'More or less level surfaces of calcareous rock of of lowlands, hills and low mountains of the boreonemoral and boreal zones of the Palaearctic, in particular alvars of the eastern Fenno-Scandian boreonemoral zone occupied by epilithic lichen communities of unit 62.32, associated with debris swards, calcareous grasslands and paucispecific nemoral fissure communities of units 34.1151, 34.317 and 62.1B1.', '(Wolkinger and Plank, 1981; Nordiska ministerradet, 1984: unit 5.1.5.1a [p.]; Summerfield, 1991; Påhlsson, 1994: unit 5.1.5.1a [p.]).');
