    'Limestone rocks and cliffs of the alpine to montane levels of high mountains of the mediterranean, nemoral, boreonemoral and boreal zones of the Palaearctic, harbouring specialized alpine chasmophyte communities.', '(Ellenberg, 1988: 448-460; Mohorovicic, 1996; Bozicevic, 1996; Puytorac y al., 1997).');
