    'Siliceous rocks and cliffs of lowlands, hills and low mountains of the nemoral zone of the Palaearctic, harbouring impoverished, paucispecific, fissure communities.', '(De Zuttere and Théatre, 1975: 28-35; Ellenberg, 1988: 452-453). ');
