    'Communities of alpine and subalpine calcareous springs of the Caucasus, with [Cardamine uliginosa], [Cardamine raphanifolia], [Primula auriculata], [Epilobium algidum], [Veronica beccabunga], [Carex orbicularis].', '(Korotkov y al., 1991: 252-253).');
