    'Inland dunes, unvegetated or colonized by species-poor grassland communities dominated by [Leymus arenarius] or [Festuca cryophila], with [Equisetum boreale], [Silene uniflora], [Silene maritima], [Armeria maritima].', '(Nordiska ministerradet, 1984: unit 4.1.2.9b; Hadac, 1985a: 145-148; Hadac, 1985b; Påhlsson, 1994: unit 4.1.3.1b; Einarsson, 1994: 187; Gudmundsson and Kjartansson, 1996: 54).');
